0of%20farmland.%3Cp%3ETed%20Soqui%2FCorbis%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-bill-gates-spends-fortune%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBill%20Gates'%20net%20worth%3C%2Fa%3E%20can%20change%20by%20the%20millions%20in%20any%20given%20day%20as%20markets%20rise%20and%20fall%2C%20but%20it%20is%20usually%20near%20%24160%20billion%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Bloomberg%20Billionaires%20Index.%20That%20places%20him%20in%20the%20bottom%20half%20of%20the%20top%2010%20richest%20people%20in%20the%20world.%20As%20noted%2C%20he%20achieved%20the%20top%20title%20in%201995%20and%20maintained%20it%20most%20years%20up%20until%202017.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGates%20has%20less%20wealth%20today%20largely%20because%20he%20has%20given%20so%20much%20of%20it%20away%20in%20the%20name%20of%20philanthropy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbill-gates-house-real-estate-property-portfolio-list-settle-washington%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBill%20Gates'%20primary%20property%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%2066%2C000%20square%20foot%20mansion%20in%20Medina%2C%20Washington%2C%20which%20is%20just%20east%20of%20Seattle%2C%20across%20Lake%20Washington.%20Construction%20took%20seven%20years%20and%20involved%20a%20team%20of%20300%20workers.%20There%20are%20six%20kitchens%20and%2024%20bathrooms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbill-gates-defends-farmland-purchases-there-isnt-%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGates%20also%20owns%20vast%20swathes%20of%20farmland%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20totaling%20approximately%20275%2C000%20acres.%20For%20comparison%2C%20all%20five%20boroughs%20of%20New%20York%20City%20cover%20just%20193%2C700%20acres.%20During%20a%20Reddit%20Q%26amp%3BA%20session%20(called%20an%20%26quot%3BAMA%26quot%3B%20for%20%26quot%3Bask%20me%20anything%26quot%3B)%2C%20Gates%20explained%20the%20massive%20holdings%2C