a%20custom%20to%20violate%20the%20Assembly's%20tradition%20and%20called%20his%20actions%20%26quot%3Bchildish%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BAccording%20to%20the%20Constitution%2C%20it%20is%20a%20tradition%20of%20legislative%20democracy%20for%20the%20state%20governor%20to%20read%20the%20government's%20address%20at%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20year!%20He%20has%20made%20it%20his%20custom%20to%20violate%20it.%20It%20is%20childish%20that%20the%20governor%2C%20who%20has%20cut%20out%20what%20was%20there%20and%20added%20what%20was%20not%2C%20has%20gone%20without%20reading%20it%20this%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20passages%20skipped%20by%20the%20Governor%20in%20his%20earlier%20speeches%20in%20the%20Assembly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDoubling%20down%2C%20the%20DMK%20chief%20yesterday%20told%20the%20House%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Governor%20comes%20to%20the%20Assembly%20but%20returns%20without%20addressing%20the%20House.%20That's%20why%20I%20had%20said%20his%20actions%20were%20childish.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20the%20Governor%20is%20unable%20to%20digest%20the%20fact%20that%20Tamil%20Nadu%20is%20developing.%20I%20may%20be%20an%20ordinary%20person%20but%20this%20Legislative%20Assembly%20came%20into%20existence%20due%20to%20the%20feelings%20of%20crore%20of%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Stalin%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20Assembly%20%26quot%3Bshould%20not%20see%20such%20things%20again%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHitting%20back%2C%20the%20Raj%20Bhavan's%20official%20handle%20posted%20on%20X%20today%2C%20%26quot%3BThiru%20%40mkstalin%20asserts%20that%20insisting%20on%20due%20respect%20to%20the%20National%20Anthem%20and%20doing%20fundamental%20duties%20enshrined%20in%20the%20Constitution%20is%20%26quot%3Babsurd%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bchildish%26quot%3B.%20Thanks%20for%20betraying%20the%20true%20intentions%20of%20the%20coalition%20of%20interests%20and%20ideologies%20to%20which%20he%20is%20a%20leader%20that%20does%20not%20accept%20and%20respect%20Bharat%20as%20a%20nation%20and%20Her%20Constitution.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSuch%20arrogance%20is%20not%20good.%20Please%20do%20not%20forget%20that%20Bharat%20is%20the%20supreme%20Mother%20and%20the%20Constitution%20the%20supreme%20faith%20for%20her%20children.%20They%20will%20not%20like%20or%20tolerate%20such%20brazen%20insult%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGovernor%20Ravi%20and%20the%20MK%20Stalin%20government%20have%20shared%20frosty%20ties%20ever%20since%20he%20took%20over%20in%202021.%20The%20DMK%20government%20has%20accused%20him%20of%20acting%20like%20a%20BJP%20spokesperson%20and%20blocking%20Bills%20and%20appointments.%20The%20Governor%20has%20said%20the%20Constitution%20empowers%20him%20to%20withhold%20his%20assent%20to%20legislation.%20The%20dispute%20between%20the%20Raj%20Bhavan%20and%20state%20government%20has%20also%20reached%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20and%20the%20Rashtrapati%20Bhavan.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736674260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-06%2F3j6upi3g_mk-stalin-rn-ravi-stalin-ravi-ani_625x300_30_June_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftamil-nadu-governor-rn-ravi-mk-stalin-such-arrogance-is-not-good-tamil-nadu-governor-hits-back-at-mk-stalin-7456327%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Hitting%20out%20at%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Chief%20Minister%20MK%20Stalin%20for%20his%20%26quot%3Bchildish%26quot%3B%20jab%20amid%20the%20National%20Anthem%20row%2C%20Governor%20RN%20Ravi%20has%20said%20%26quot%3Bsuch%20arrogance%20is%20not%20good%26quot%3B%20and%20warned%20that%20the%20country%20would%20not%20tolerate%20such%20%26quot%3Bbrazen%20insult%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20anthem%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Here's%20how%20single%20women%20are%20successfully%20navigating%20an%20otherwise%20brutal%20market%20for%20first-time%20homebuyers%22%2C%22con