r%2C%20Amazon%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-delays-full-rto-some-staff-workspace-shortages-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20delayed%20RTO%20requirements%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20some%20workers%20because%20of%20a%20dearth%20of%20office%20space%20and%20a%20need%20to%20reconfigure%20some%20setups.%20At%20AT%26amp%3BT%2C%20which%20has%20also%20called%20workers%20back%2C%20employees%20at%20some%20offices%20have%20had%20trouble%20snagging%20workspaces%20in%20the%20new%20year%20and%20have%20resorted%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fatt-begins-5-days-office-mandate-desks-parking-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eworking%20in%20a%20dining%20area%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20at%20conference%20tables%2C%20BI%20recently%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20push%20to%20populate%20hot%20desks%20and%20cubicles%20comes%20as%20many%20leaders%20appear%20fed%20up%20with%20talking%20about%20working%20from%20home.%20Some%20chiefs%20might%20see%20RTO%20mandates%20from%20high-profile%20companies%20like%20Amazon%20as%20the%20cover%20they%20need%20to%20issue%20similar%20orders.%20Yet%2C%20in%20the%20effort%20to%20bring%20workers%20back%2C%20not%20every%20office%20was%20ready%20for%20the%20influx.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTowards%20the%20end%20of%20last%20year%2C%20it%20became%20clear%20that%20CEOs%20were%20just%20done%2C%26quot%3B%20Dan%20Kaplan%2C%20senior%20client%20partner%20at%20the%20recruiting%20firm%20Korn%20Ferry%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20he%20said%2C%20some%20organizations%20didn't%20do%20sufficient%20prep%20work%20to%20call%20everyone%20back%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20after%20cutting%20office%20space%20during%20the%20depths%20of%20the%20pandemic%20when%20those%20who%20could%20do%20so%20logged%20on%20from%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20Kaplan%20said%2C%20for%20some%20CEOs%2C%20the%20thinking%20goes%2C%20%26quot%3BWe'll%20clean%20up%20the%20mess%20later%2C%20but%20for%20now%2C%20we%20are%20ripping%20that%20Band-Aid%20and%20getting%20people%20the%20heck%20back%20in%20the%20office%2C%20come%20hell%20or%20high%20water%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ab648281-6ee6-4987-9f3f-3bd1a53b616a%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAI%20could%20be%20adding%20uncertainty%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20employers%20are%20shifting%20back%20to%20the%20office%20even%20as%20they%20don't%20know%20how%20much%20space%20they'll%20ultimately%20need%20in%20the%20next%20few%20years%20because%20artificial%20intelligence%20could%20one%20day%20replace%20some%20workers%2C%20Dan%20Root%2C%20head%20of%20global%20strategic%20alliances%20at%20Barco%20ClickShare%2C%20which%20makes%20tech%20used%20in%20office%20meeting%20rooms%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20starts%20to%20really%20make%20you%20question%2C%20'OK%2C%20well%2C%20how%20much%20square%20footage%20am%20I%20going%20to%20be%20committing%20to%3F'%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20the%20World%20Economic%20Forum%20reported%20that%20in%20a%20survey%20of%20companies%20worldwide%2C%2041%25%20said%20they%20planned%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frecent-company-layoffs-laying-off-workers-2025%23%3A~%3Atext%3DIn%2520a%2520recent%2520World%2520Economic%2Cthe%2520rise%2520of%2520artificial%2520intelligence.%26amp%3Btext%3DCompanies%2520such%2520as%2520Dropbox%252C%2520Google%2Cjob%2520cuts%2520related%2520to%2520AI.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecut%20their%20workforce%3C%2Fa%3E%20during%20the%20next%20five%20years%20in%20instances%20where%20AI%20could%20take%20on%20the%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20challenge%3A%20Some%20employers%20adjusted%20for%20hybrid%20setups%20%E2%80%94%20and%20added%20places%20for%20couches%20and%20other%20amenities%20to%20draw%20workers%20back%20to%20the%20office%20%E2%80%94%20that%20worked%20well%20when%20offices%20weren't%20always%20fully%20staffed.%20Yet%20now%20that%20more%20workers%20are%20coming%20back%2C%20space%20can%20be%20tight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENick%20Romito%2C%20CEO%20of%20VTS%2C%20a%20commercial%20real%20estate%20technology%20firm%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20two%20to%20two-and-a-half%20years%20ago%2C%20many%20employers%20looking%20for%20office%20space%20might%20have%20been%20shopping%20for%20less%20square%20footage%20than%20they'd%20need%20to%20accommodate%20a%20full%20staff.%20Many%20employers%20optimized%20for%20hybrid%2C%20yet%20that%20only%20works%20if%20people%20don't%20show%20up%20at%20the%20same%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20trying%20to%20adjust%20for%20that%20a%20few%20years%20ago%20has%20now%20hurt%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20took%2010%2C000%20feet%20when%20they%20really%20needed%2015%2C000.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2285a4a09e-0c17-4f67-b08a-e8c05a027c6b%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EEmployers%20are%20catching%20up%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20AT%26amp%3BT%20spokesman%20told%20BI%20that%20the%20company%20is%20%26quot%3Bconstantly%20enhancing%26quot%3B%20its%20facilities%20to%20make%20them%20desirable%20and%20ensure%20workers%20have%20what%20they%20need.%20Office%20seating%20for%2070%25%20to%2080%25%20of%20employees%20is%20an%20industry%20standard%2C%20given%20the%20variables%20that%20can%20affect%20attendance%20on%20any%20given%20day%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAT%26amp%3BT%20is%20%26quot%3Bquickly%20working%20through%20the%20challenges%20in%20select%20locations%20so%20the%20rest%20of%20our%20employees%20are%20best%20positioned%20to%20support%20their%20coworkers%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20Amazon%20spokesperson%20told%20BI%20that%20as%20of%20last%20week%2C%20the%20%26quot%3Boverwhelming%20majority%26quot%3B%20of%20its%20workers%20had%20dedicated%20workspaces%20and%20have%20returned%20to%20the%20office%20full%20time.%20Among%20Amazon's%20hundreds%20of%20offices%20globally%2C%20%26quot%3Bonly%20a%20relatively%20small%20number%26quot%3B%20aren't%20yet%20ready%20for%20workers%20to%20return%20five%20days%20a%20week%2C%20the%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20reason%20some%20CEOs%20might%20feel%20comfortable%20calling%20workers%20back%20to%20the%20office%20is%20that%20while%20the%20overall%20US%20jobless%20rate%20remains%20low%2C%20it's%20often%20still%20a%20challenging%20job%20market%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhite-collar-recession-hiring-slump-jobs-tech-industry-applications-rejection-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewhite-collar%20workers%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20difficulty%20many%20might%20face%20in%20finding%20other%20work%20could%20mean%20they're%20at%20the%20mercy%20of%20their%20employer's%20plans%2C%20Dan%20Schawbel%2C%20managing%20partner%20of%20the%20research%20firm%20Workplace%20Intelligence%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20might%20have%20no%20choice%20but%20to%20return%20to%20the%20office%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20though%20added%20that%20in%20some%20cases%2C%20workers%20won't%20be%20able%20to%20comply%20because%20of%20family%20circumstances%20or%20owning%20a%20home%20too%20far%20from%20the%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWorksites%20could%20get%20crowded%20if%20more%20workers%20comply%20with%20RTO%20orders%20than%20employers%20might%20have%20expected.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BStrategic%20companies%20have%20made%20these%20calculations%2C%20but%20there%20is%20room%20for%20error%2C%26quot%3B%20Schawbel%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20workers%20do%20quit%20because%20they're%20unhappy%20with%20the%20RTO%2C%20Korn%20Ferry's%20Kaplan%20said%2C%20it's%20an%20easy%20way%20for%20employers%20to%20reduce%20costs%20without%20generating%20negative%20headlines%20around%20job%20cuts%20or%20incurring%20related%20expenses%20like%20severance%20or%20extended%20benefits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20some%20of%20them%2C%20it's%20a%20free%20layoff%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20have%20something%20to%20share%20about%20your%20RTO%20experience%3F%20Business%20Insider%20would%20like%20to%20hear%20from%20you.%20Email%20our%20workplace%20team%20from%20a%20nonwork%20device%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Athegrind%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Ethegrind%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20with%20your%20story%2C%20or%20to%20ask%20for%20one%20of%20our%20reporter's%20Signal%20numbers.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-rto-fail-not-ready-workers-return-to-office-2025-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736674022000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67819ebf88b000981b4a8066%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-rto-fail-not-ready-workers-return-to-office-2025-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22CEOs'%20pushes%20to%20get%20workers%20back%20to%20the%20office%20mean%20some%20are%20returning%20to%20a%20lack%20of%20parking%20or%20desk%20space%2C%20with%20companies%20including%20Amazon%20delaying.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22tparadis%40businessinsider.com%20(Tim%20Paradis)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A20%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-rto-fail-not-ready-workers-return-to-office-2025-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Masaba%20Gupta%E2%80%99s%20sis-in-law%20loses%20home%20to%20LA%20wildfire%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736673834000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-117171237%2Cimgsize-44588.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fmasaba-guptas-sister-in-law-loses-her-home-to-la-wildfires-the-celebrity-designers-husband-satyadeep-misra-shares-an-emotional-post%2Farticleshow%2F117171214.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg