some%20ski%20patrollers'%20total%20monthly%20income.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aspenpublicradio.org%2Feconomics%2F2024-03-15%2Fsome-mountain-west-states-have-the-highest-grocery-prices-in-the-nation%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGroceries%20and%20gas%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20also%20costly%20in%20many%20mountain%20areas%20because%20of%20limited%20stores%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kunc.org%2Fnews%2F2024-02-25%2Ffuels-gold-why-colorados-mountains-are-seeing-some-of-the-highest-gas-prices-in-the-state%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehigh%20transportation%20costs%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20goods.%20A%20dozen%20eggs%20is%20just%20over%20%244%20in%20Denver%2C%20but%20nearly%20%247%20in%20Breckenridge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKyle%20Eveland%2C%2024%2C%20makes%20%2423.28%20an%20hour%20as%20a%20second-year%20ski%20patroller%20at%20Breckenridge%20Resort%20in%20Colorado.%20Before%20he%20reports%20to%20the%20mountain%20every%20morning%20to%20set%20up%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Favalanche-california-tahoe-how-man-survived-buried-in-snow-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eavalanche%20mitigation%3C%2Fa%3E%20equipment%2C%20Eveland%20said%20he%20shovels%20snow%20for%20a%20nearby%20property.%20He%20works%20a%20full-time%20construction%20job%20over%20the%20summer%2C%20when%20the%20ski%20resort%20is%20closed%2C%20and%20recently%20began%20a%20part-time%20role%20pumping%20concrete%20between%20his%20patrol%20shifts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20love%20to%20do%20what%20I%20love%20every%20day%20and%20take%20the%20sacrifice%20of%20not%20making%20a%20lot%20of%20money%20doing%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20%26quot%3BI%20pretty%20much%20live%20paycheck%20to%20paycheck%20in%20the%20winter.%20It%20would%20be%20super%2C%20super%20tight%20if%20I%20just%20patrolled.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERight%20now%2C%20Eveland%20lives%20in%20Breckenridge%20with%20seven%20other%20roommates.%20He%20said%20he%20took%20a%20pay%20cut%20when%20he%20decided%20to%20join%20ski%20patrol%2C%20despite%20the%20job%20requiring%20significant%20training.%20He%20previously%20worked%20at%20Breckenridge%20as%20a%20chairlift%20operator.%20Eveland%20said%20he%20may%20need%20to%20leave%20his%20patrolling%20job%20if%20he%20wants%20to%20afford%20a%20down%20payment%20or%20support%20a%20family%20in%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20got%20my%20EMT%20license%20and%20that%20got%20me%20a%20single%20dollar%20raise%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETate%20Finigan's%20experience%20is%20similar.%20The%2026-year-old%20recently%20began%20his%20third%20season%20as%20a%20ski%20patroller%20in%20Park%20City.%20Finigan%20commutes%20from%20Salt%20Lake%20City%2C%20over%20a%2030-mile%20drive%2C%20every%20day%20because%20he%20can't%20afford%20housing%20in%20Park%20City.%20When%20he's%20not%20on%20the%20mountain%2C%20Finigan%20babysits%20and%20walks%20dogs%2C%20and%20previously%20picked%20up%20shifts%20as%20a%20bartender.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20been%20really%20hard%20to%20try%20and%20live%20in%20this%20community%20that%20we%20all%20so%20badly%20want%20to%20be%20a%20part%20of%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kyle%20Eveland%2C%2024%2C%20works%20as%20a%20ski%20patroller%20at%20Colorado's%20Breckenridge%20Resort.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F678031998951662c9f1f7caa%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222648%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKyle%20Eveland%2C%2024%2C%20is%20a%20second-year%20ski%20patroller%20at%20Breckenridge%20Resort%20in%20Colorado.%3Cp%3EPhoto%20Courtesy%20of%20Kyle%20Eveland%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226fd346e3-a61d-45f2-a49c-75495f58e3c7%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EIn%20a%20profession%20that%20relies%20on%20experience%2C%20seasoned%20patrollers%20aren't%20sure%20they%20can%20stay%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESki%20patrolling%