%20weren't%20able%20to%20confirm%20your%20identity%20from%20the%20video%20you%20submitted%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20message%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20can%20submit%20a%20new%20video%20and%20we'll%20review%20it%20again.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20fun%20as%20this%20game%20sounded%2C%20I%20had%20other%20things%20to%20take%20care%20of.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20figured%20that%20suddenly%20switching%20phone%20numbers%20would%20result%20in%20some%20headaches%2C%20but%20I%20didn't%20foresee%20how%20complicated%20it%20would%20actually%20become.%20From%20Lyft%20and%20Cash%20App%20to%20Instagram%20and%20Amazon%2C%20I%20suddenly%20had%20to%20jump%20through%20logistical%20hoops%20that%20varied%20from%20one%20platform%20to%20the%20next%20to%20verify%20my%20flesh-and-blood%20identity%20and%20regain%20access%20to%20my%20digital%20life.%20Confirming%20my%20identity%20became%20a%20part-time%20job.%20And%20as%20I%20learned%20the%20hard%20way%2C%20fellow%20human%20beings%20who%20could%20help%20me%20sort%20things%20out%20were%20hard%20to%20come%20by.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20origin%20of%20text-message-based%20two-factor%20authentication%20goes%20back%20as%20far%20as%20the%201990s%2C%20it%20wasn't%20until%20the%20early%202010s%20that%20it%20really%20started%20to%20proliferate.%20As%20more%20people%20bought%20smartphones%2C%20it%20seemed%20convenient%20to%20use%20a%20person's%20phone%20number%20as%20a%20way%20to%20confirm%20their%20identity.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20the%20growing%20frequency%20and%20sophistication%20of%20data%20breaches%20and%20cyberattacks%20rendered%20traditional%20passwords%20nearly%20useless%2C%20prompting%20then-President%20Barack%20Obama%20to%20write%20an%20op-ed%20in%20The%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%20in%202016%20imploring%20citizens%20to%20%26quot%3Bmove%20beyond%20passwords%26quot%3B%20and%20embrace%20additional%20layers%20of%20security%20to%20protect%20their%20data.%20Even%20in%202024%2C%20hackable%20passwords%20like%20%26quot%3B1234%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bpassword%26quot%3B%20remained%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.axios.com%2F2024%2F11%2F14%2Fcommon-passwords-2024-list%3Futm%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ealarmingly%20common%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20requiring%20people%20to%20take%20an%20extra%20step%20(or%20two)%20to%20verify%20themselves%2C%20multifactor%20authentication%20offers%20a%20massive%20security%20improvement%20over%20the%20traditional%20password.%20Thanks%20to%20remote%20work%2C%20MFA%20adoption%20is%20on%20the%20rise%3A%2064%25%20of%20people%20using%20Okta%20use%20some%20form%20of%20multifactor%20authentication%2C%20a%202023%20report%20by%20the%20company%20found.%20Before%20the%20pandemic%2C%20it%20was%2035%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20its%20benefits%2C%20the%20system%20developed%20a%20serious%20flaw%20somewhere%20along%20the%20way%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftwitter-blue-sms-two-factor-authentication-subscription-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESMS-based%20two-factor%20authentication%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20relies%20on%20calling%20or%20texting%20someone's%20phone%20to%20verify%20their%20identity.%20Unlike%20MFA%20methods%20that%20rely%20on%20an%20authenticator%20app%2C%20text-based%20authentication%20is%20arguably%20the%20least%20secure%20way%20to%20verify%20someone's%20identity.%20Unfortunately%2C%20it's%20also%20one%20of%20the%20most%20common.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20often%20see%20that%20less%20mature%20organizations%20have%20standardized%20on%20using%20that%20SMS-based%20code%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Cristian%20Rodriguez%2C%20the%20field%20chief%20technical%20officer%20for%20the%20Americas%20at%20the%20cybersecurity%20firm%20CrowdStrike.%20Apple%2C%20Google%2C%20Zoom%2C%20Slack%2C%20Dropbox%2C%20PayPal%2C%20and%20most%20major%20US%20banks%20and%20universities%20are%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2F2fawebsites.github.io%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elong%20list%20of%20sites%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20still%20use%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20also%20easy%20to%20intercept%2C%26quot%3B%20Rodriguez%20said%20of%20the%20method.%20%26quot%3BSIM%20swapping%20is%20a%20really%20easy%20way%20to%20circumvent%20that%20as%20an%20attacker.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcredit-card-phone-theft-sim-swap-identity-theft-investigation-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESIM-swapping%20attack%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20hacker%20can%20gain%20control%20of%20someone's%20phone%20number%20and%20wreak%20havoc%20on%20their%20lives.%20From%20their%20bank%20and%20social%20media%20accounts%20to%20credit%20cards%20stored%20in%20digital%20wallets%20like%20Apple%20Pay%2C%20the%20amount%20of%20access%20a%20cybercriminal%20can%20gain%20is%20staggering.%20It%20shows%20just%20how%20thoroughly%20our%20lives%20are%20tied%20to%20our%20phone%20numbers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-treasury-computer-hack-china-beyondtrust-cybersecurity-breach-salt-typhoon-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehackers%20aligned%20with%20the%20Chinese%20government%3C%2Fa%3E%20managed%20to%20gain%20access%20to%20US%20phones%20via%20their%20telecommunication%20networks%20in%20a%20massive%20hack%20dubbed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-salt-typhoon-hack-china-phone-security-phone-encryption-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESalt%20Typhoon%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20the%20federal%20government%20says%20is%20among%20the%20worst%20in%20the%20nation's%20history.%20While%20the%20exact%20origins%20and%20overall%20impact%20of%20Salt%20Typhoon%20are%20still%20being%20investigated%2C%20experts%20say%20that%20the%20two-year%20infiltration%20could%20have%20affected%20millions%20of%20Americans.%20In%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20attack%2C%20which%20was%20first%20reported%20in%20October%2C%20the%20feds%20are%20advising%20people%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fways-to-protect-yourself-from-hacks-or-scams-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estop%20using%20SMS-based%20authentication%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnlike%20our%20fingerprints%20or%20faces%2C%20our%20phone%20number%20is%20not%20a%20permanent%20feature%20of%20our%20identity.%20It's%20just%20a%20sequence%20of%20digits%20randomly%20assigned%20to%20us%20by%20a%20cell%20provider%20when%20we%20sign%20up.%20If%20we%20stop%20paying%2C%20switch%20mobile%20providers%2C%20or%20move%20to%20a%20new%20country%2C%20the%20number%20is%20no%20longer%20ours.%20Even%20an%20email%20address%20%E2%80%94%20in%20my%20case%2C%20a%2020-year-old%20Gmail%20account%20that%20I'm%20certain%20will%20continue%20receiving%20marketing%20promotions%20long%20after%20I'm%20dead%20%E2%80%94%20would%20make%20a%20more%20reliable%20long-term%20indicator%20of%20who%20I%20am%20than%20my%20phone%20number.%20After%20all%2C%20my%20email%20address%20will%20never%20be%20reassigned.%20It's%20mine.%20My%20phone%20number%20%E2%80%94%20along%20with%20the%20roughly%2035%20million%20numbers%20that%20get%20reassigned%20each%20year%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Federal%20Communications%20Commission%20%E2%80%94%20is%20another%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFew%20companies%20seem%20to%20recognize%20the%20problem%3A%20In%20early%202023%2C%20X%20decided%20to%20end%20support%20for%20SMS-based%20two-factor%20authentication%20for%20nonverified%20users%2C%20citing%20its%20weakness.%20Following%20major%20breaches%2C%20tech%20giants%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-two-step-verification-by-default-passwordless-2021-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogle%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Microsoft%20have%20also%20begun%20to%20make%20moves%20away%20from%20SMS%20authentication.%20Still%2C%20X%20stands%20alone%20among%20major%20social%20media%20platforms%20in%20abandoning%20it%20altogether%20%E2%80%94%20a%20fact%20that%20I%20had%20to%20learn%20the%20hard%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20most%20cases%2C%20regaining%20access%20to%20my%20accounts%20was%20simple.%20My%20bank%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20just%20required%20a%20quick%20phone%20call%20to%20a%20customer%20service%20agent%20to%20confirm%20my%20identity%2C%20bypass%20MFA%2C%20update%20my%20phone%20number%2C%20and%20reset%20my%20password.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstagram%2C%20an%20operation%20notably%20larger%20and%20more%20resourced%20than%20the%20small%20credit%20union%20I%20bank%20with%2C%20did%20not%20offer%20a%20customer%20service%20hotline.%20Instead%2C%20after%20about%20half%20a%20dozen%20clicks%20from%20Instagram's%20login%20screen%2C%20I%20found%20my%20way%20into%20the%20depths%20of%20a%20customer%20service%20FAQ%20page%20that%20suggested%20I%20send%20a%20video%20selfie.%20I%20had%20to%20send%20several%20videos%20into%20the%20automated%20void%20before%20the%20app%20caved%20and%20let%20me%20back%20into%20my%20account.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20Amazon%20account%2C%20which%20includes%20services%20like%20Audible%2C%20Alexa%2C%20and%20Whole%20Foods%20shopping%2C%20proved%20a%20surprisingly%20impenetrable%20fortress.%20After%20clicking%20my%20way%20through%20a%20labyrinth%20of%20links%2C%20I%20eventually%20reached%20a%20prompt%20that%20asked%20me%20to%20upload%20a%20photo%20of%20my%20passport%20to%20verify%20my%20identity.%20After%20not%20hearing%20anything%20for%20a%20week%2C%20I%20tried%20again.%20A%20few%20months%20later%2C%20Amazon%20let%20me%20back%20in.%20%3Cspan%3E(Instagram%20and%20Amazon%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20multiple%20requests%20for%20comment.)%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThanks%20to%20the%20ongoing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-chatbots-customer-service-call-center-annoying-problems-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI-ification%20of%20customer%20service%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20growing%20use%20of%20chatbots%2C%20the%20privilege%20of%20speaking%20with%20a%20real%20person%20is%20increasingly%20rare.%20To%20this%20day%2C%20I'm%20unable%20to%20verify%20my%20LinkedIn%20profile.%20Even%20after%20asking%20for%20my%20current%20phone%20number%2C%20the%20identity-verification%20platform%20used%20by%20LinkedIn%2C%20Clear%2C%20continues%20to%20text%20a%20six-digit%20code%20to%20my%20%3Cem%3Eold%20%3C%2Fem%3Ephone%20number%2C%20which%20it%20somehow%20summons%20from%20the%20cloud.%20Of%20course%2C%20there's%20no%20one%20to%20speak%20with%20to%20resolve%20the%20issue.%20Oh%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGetting%20locked%20out%20of%20social%20networks%20and%20online%20shops%20is%20extremely%20annoying.%20But%20it's%20nothing%20compared%20to%20the%20nightmare%20I%20suffered%20through%20when%20I%20tried%20to%20sign%20up%20for%20unemployment%20benefits%20after%20getting%20laid%20off%20from%20my%20journalism%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20government%20of%20Pennsylvania%20uses%20the%20aptly%20named%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fidme-identity-verification-irs-unemployment-facial-recognition-staff-layoffs-economy-2022-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EID.me%20%3C%2Fa%3Eservice%20to%20handle%20its%20website%20login%20and%20identity%20verification%20for%20services%20like%20unemployment.%20On%20its%20website%2C%20ID.me%20boasts%20integrations%20with%2019%20federal%20agencies%2C%2035%20healthcare-related%20organizations%2C%20and%20more%20than%20600%20online%20stores%20in%20its%20mission%20to%20empower%20consumers%20with%20%26quot%3Ba%20single%20log-in%20that%20lets%20you%20easily%20prove%20you're%20you.%26quot%3B%20There's%20just%20one%20problem%3A%20ID.me%20ties%20your%20digital%20identity%20to%20your%20phone%20number.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20tried%20logging%20in%20to%20the%20Pennsylvania%20unemployment%20site%20to%20claim%20my%20benefits%2C%20I%20discovered%20I%20already%20had%20an%20ID.me%20account%20%E2%80%94%20presumably%20from%20some%20other%20government%20site%20I%20had%20previously%20accessed.%20That%20account%2C%20of%20course%2C%20was%20linked%20to%20my%20old%20phone%20number.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWithout%20access%20to%20that%20number%20%E2%80%94%20and%20having%20no%20clue%20what%20my%20password%20might%20have%20been%20%E2%80%94%20my%20only%20option%20was%20to%20submit%20a%20request%20to%20bypass%20MFA%20and%20regain%20access%20to%20my%20ID.me%20account%20through%20the%20company's%20customer%20service%20help%20desk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20I%20got%20an%20automated%20confirmation%20email%20from%20Roy%2C%20the%20self-described%20%26quot%3Bvirtual%20agent%26quot%3B%20at%20ID.me%2C%20my%20request%20went%20ignored%20for%2048%20hours.%20After%20multiple%20follow-ups%20and%20a%20great%20deal%20of%20patience%2C%20I%20was%20finally%20able%20to%20set%20up%20a%20phone%20screening%20with%20a%20real%20human.%20Ten%20days%20after%20my%20initial%20request%2C%20I%20was%20on%20the%20phone%20with%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcustomer-service-phone-calls-paid-status-symbol-luxury-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecustomer%20service%20agent%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20emailed%20me%20some%20instructions%3A%20Fill%20out%20a%20few%20forms%20and%20send%20them%20back%20along%20with%20digital%20scans%20of%20my%20passport%20and%20Social%20Security%20card.%20Normally%2C%20sending%20such%20sensitive%20information%20over%20email%20would%20give%20me%20pause%2C%20but%20in%20this%20case%2C%20the%20ID.me%20customer%20service%20agent%20was%20holding%20my%20identity%20and%20my%20financial%20security%20hostage%2C%20so%20I%20was%20inclined%20to%20do%20whatever%20he%20asked.%20I%20could%20only%20hope%20that%20ID.me's%20cybersecurity%20practices%20were%20more%20robust%20than%20its%20customer%20service%20operation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%2030%20days%20of%20submitting%20and%20resubmitting%20various%20identifying%20documents%2C%20I%20was%20finally%20able%20to%20log%20in%20to%20my%20account.%20By%20then%2C%20I%20had%20taken%20care%20of%20my%20unemployment%20needs%20the%20old-fashioned%20way%3A%20filing%20my%20applicat