merican%20conflict%20%E2%80%94%20a%20primarily%20maritime%20theatre%20%E2%80%94%20as%20they%20do%20in%20Europe%20(although%20both%20capabilities%20have%20a%20role%20in%20each%20theatre)%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20analyst%20Sidharth%20Kaushal%20in%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Frusi.org%2Fexplore-our-research%2Fpublications%2Fwhitehall-reports%2Fimpact-taiwan-strait-crisis-european-defence%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereport%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20for%20the%20Royal%20United%20Services%20Institute.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAmerica%20has%20had%20to%20cope%20with%20the%20dichotomy%20between%20the%20Atlantic%20and%20the%20Pacific%20since%20World%20War%20II.%20In%20that%20war%2C%20the%20European%20theater%20was%20a%20ground%20conflict%20fought%20between%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbattle-of-the-bulge-allies-crush-the-nazis-last-great-offensive-2017-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehuge%20mechanized%20armies%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20hordes%20of%20land-based%20aircraft%2C%20albeit%20with%20a%20smaller%20naval%20component%20in%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbritish-plan-to-hunt-german-uboats-from-ice-aircraft-carrier-2021-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esea%20battle%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20resupply%20Britain.%20The%20Pacific%20theater%20was%20a%20naval%20and%20air%20conflict%20fought%20among%20scattered%20islands%2C%20which%20put%20a%20premium%20on%20aircraft%20carriers%2C%20submarines%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbattles-of-iwo-jima-okinawa-made-us-reconsider-japan-invasion-2021-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Emobile%20amphibious%20units%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20such%20as%20the%20US%20Marine%20Corps.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECompounding%20the%20problem%20is%20that%20modern%20armies%20and%20weapons%20are%20expensive.%20The%20US%20could%20afford%20to%20fight%20a%20two-front%20war%20in%201941.%20Building%20a%20military%20sufficient%20to%20simultaneously%20defend%20Taiwan%20and%20Europe%20today%20would%20be%20ruinous%2C%20one%20of%20the%20many%20reasons%20the%20US%20maintains%20strong%20alliances%20in%20both%20regions.%20To%20be%20sure%2C%20the%20US%20backs%20Taiwan's%20independent%20government%2C%20but%20it's%20unclear%20whether%20it%20would%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbiden-us-would-use-military-if-china-attacked-taiwan-2022-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ecommit%20forces%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20Taiwan's%20defense.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20Kaushal%20believes%20that%20the%20problem%20may%20be%20manageable%20by%20focusing%20on%20a%20couple%20of%20key%20variables.%20In%20particular%2C%20the%20success%20of%20an%20invasion%20of%20Taiwan%20depends%20upon%20China's%20ability%20to%20achieve%20sufficient%20air%20and%20naval%20superiority%20to%20protect%20the%20amphibious%20fleet%20ferrying%20assault%20troops%20and%20the%20logistics%20they%20depend%20upon.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BThe%20crux%20of%20any%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-plans-turn-taiwan-strait-into-drone-hellscape-against-china-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edefense%20of%20Taiwan%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20will%20be%20denying%20it%20this%20superiority%2C%26quot%3B%20Kaushal%20argued.%20%26quot%3BIf%20this%20is%20achieved%2C%20it%20is%20likely%20that%20Taiwan's%20forces%20can%20mount%20a%20successful%20forward%20defense%20of%20likely%20landing%20sites%20on%20the%20island%2C%20making%20a%20protracted%20defense%20and%20the%20subsequent%20flow%20of%20US%20forces%20superfluous.%20If%20not%2C%20the%20battle%20will%20likely%20end%20before%20either%20of%20these%20things%20can%20be%20considered.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20turn%2C%20this%20means%20that%20only%20some%20American%20military%20capabilities%20would%20be%20relevant%2C%20especially%20anti-ship%20missiles%2C%20submarines%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-taiwan-could-use-sea-mines-to-stop-chinese-invasion-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Emines%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftaiwan-is-one-upping-ukraines-navy-to-defeat-a-chinese-invasion-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ENaval%20drones%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20like%20those%20wielded%20by%20Ukraine%2C%20may%20also%20prove%20powerful%20weapons%20to%20attack%20a%20Chinese%20armada.%20Conversely%2C%20heavy%20armor%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20capacity%20to%20transport%20it%20%E2%80%94%20would%20be%20paramount%20in%20supporting%20NATO%20against%20a%20Russian%20attack.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20sinking%20a%20Chinese%20fleet%20will%20require%20SEAD%20(suppression%20of%20enemy%20air%20defenses)%20missions%20against%20defensive%20systems%20protecting%20the%20invasion%20convoys.%20And%20it's%20there%20that%20the%20difference%20between%20the%20Atlantic%20and%20Pacific%20becomes%20manifest.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22US%20attack%20submarines%20are%20more%20needed%20in%20the%20Pacific%20than%20to%20defeat%20enemy%20armies%20in%20Europe%2C%20a%20seapower%20expert%20argues.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F677ffbb150dfd88e193da31e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221429%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUS%20attack%20submarines%20are%20more%20needed%20in%20the%20Pacific%20than%20to%20defeat%20enemy%20armies%20in%20Europe%2C%20a%20seapower%20expert%20argues.%3Cp%3EMC1%20Keenan%20Daniels%2FUS%20Navy%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20Europe%2C%20Russian%20ground%20forces%20would%20be%20protected%20by%20land-based%20surface-to-air%20missile%20(SAM)%20batteries%20and%20radars%2C%20which%20are%20mounted%20or%20transported%20by%20truck.%20NATO%20would%20first%20have%20to%20locate%20them%20and%20then%20strike%20them%20with%20air-launched%20anti-radar%20missiles%20such%20as%20the%20US%20AGM-88%20HARM%2C%20or%20ground%20fire%20from%20artillery%2C%20tactical%20missiles%2C%20and%20drones.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20Chinese%20invasion%20fleet%20in%20the%20narrow%20110-mile-wide%20Taiwan%20Strait%2C%20by%20contrast%2C%20would%20be%20an%20easily%20detected%20target%20and%20would%20be%20out%20of%20range%20of%20land-based%20SAMs%20on%20the%20Chinese%20mainland.%20Air%20defense%20would%20have%20to%20come%20from%20weapons%20on%20the%20Chinese%20warships%2C%20which%20can%20put%20out%20an%20impressive%20amount%20of%20firepower%20against%20hostile%20aircraft%20and%20missiles.%20China's%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-vs-chinese-navy-ticonderoga-class-type-055-destroyer-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EType%20055%20Renhai-class%20cruisers%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20for%20example%2C%20are%20equipped%20with%20112%20vertical%20launch%20tubes%20that%20can%20fire%20anti-aircraft%20or%20anti-ship%20missiles.%20The%20ships%20are%20also%20likely%20to%20be%20defended%20by%20fighter%20jets%2C%20many%20launched%20from%20airbases%20in%20China.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BSEAD%20in%20the%20European%20context%20is%20primarily%20a%20function%20of%20the%20ability%20to%20suppress%20or%20destroy%20a%20layered%20network%20of%20elusive%20and%20mobile%20ground-based%20SAM%20systems%2C%26quot%3B%20Kaushal%20wrote.%20In%20the%20Taiwan%20Strait%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20challenge%20is%20not%20that%20targets%20are%20elusive%2C%20but%20rather%20that%20they%20are%20exceedingly%20well%20defended.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESEAD%20weapons%2C%20such%20as%20the%20HARM%20missile%2C%20aren't%20really%20designed%20to%20hit%20ships.%20So%20rather%20than%20targeting%20Chinese%20air%20defenses%20specifically%2C%20the%20US%20and%20its%20allies%20should%20simply%20concentrate%20on%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-air-force-weapon-sinks-warships-cant-fight-china-navy-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esinking%20warships%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Every%20Chinese%20warship%20destroyed%20is%20one%20less%20escort%20for%20the%20troop%20ships.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20Taiwan%20war%2C%20%26quot%3BSEAD%20is%20largely%20synonymous%20with%20anti-surface%20warfare%20and%20OCA%20%5Boffensive%20counter-air%5D%2C%26quot%3B%20Kaushal%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BIf%20the%20picket%20of%20destroyers%20and%20cruisers%20protecting%20an%20invasion%20force%20suffers%20substantial%20losses%20and%20if%20%5BPeople's%20Liberation%20Army%5D%20aircraft%2C%20including%20AWACS%2C%20cannot%20freely%20operate%20over%20the%20Strait%2C%20the%20amphibious%20vessels%20on%20which%20an%20invasion%20defends%20are%20much%20less%20defensible.%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-russias-a50-command-plane-compares-to-boeing-e3-sentry-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EAdvanced%20warning%20and%20control%20aircraft%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20are%20flying%20radars%20that%20detect%20hostile%20threats%20for%20a%20wider%20force.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20similar%20dichotomy%20between%20Europe%20and%20the%20Pacific%20applies%20to%20weapons%20needed%20for%20missile%20defense.%20%26quot%3BWhile%20all%20US%20IAMD%20%5Bintegrated%20air%20and%20missile%20defense%5D%20will%20be%20missed%2C%20some%20capabilities%20will%20leave%20more%20of%20a%20gap%20than%20others%2C%26quot%3B%20Kaushal%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20Europe%2C%20the%20threat%20is%20largely%20from%20Russian%20cruise%20missiles%20and%20short-range%20ballistic%20missiles.%20Against%20these%20weapons%2C%20the%20best%20defense%20is%20blast-fragmentation%20interceptors%20%E2%80%94%20which%20detonate%20an%20explosive%20charge%20near%20the%20target%20%E2%80%94%20or%20shorter-range%20hit-to-kill%20rockets%20(which%20kinetically%20slam%20into%20a%20missile)%20such%20as%20the%20US%20PAC-3%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpatriot-performance-in-ukraine-dispels-doubts-over-abilities-experts-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Elaunched%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20from%20the%20Patriot%20air%20defense%20system.%20In%20the%20Pacific%2C%20the%20threat%20is%20from%20Chinese%20intermediate-%20and%20medium-range%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-military-china-missile-problem-getting-worse-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eballistic%20missiles%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20such%20as%20the%20DF-21%20%26quot%3Bcarrier%20killer%26quot%3B%20missile.%20Defense%20against%20them%20favors%20longer-range%2C%20high-altitude%20hit-to-kill%20interceptors%20such%20as%20the%20American%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-navy-top-interceptor-missile-heavy-price-tag-low-procurement-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ESM-3%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftop-us-missile-defense-system-in-israel-used-combat-again-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ETHAAD%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWeapons%20won't%20be%20the%20only%20precious%20commodity%20split%20between%20East%20and%20West.%20Running%20two%20regional%20wars%20comes%20with%20a%20problem%20beyond%20firepower%3A%20bra