0accepted%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20has%20said.%20%26quot%3BEverybody%20I've%20invited%20has%20accepted.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECorporates%20Line%20Up%20With%20Big%20Donations%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEager%20to%20please%20the%20new%20administration%2C%20industry%20leaders%20have%20made%20massive%20financial%20contributions%20to%20the%20inauguration%20event.%20According%20to%20a%20report%20in%20The%20New%20York%20Times%2C%20the%20inaugural%20committee%20has%20raised%20over%20170%20million%20dollars%20and%20is%20well%20on%20its%20way%20to%20crossing%20the%20200%20million%20dollar%20mark.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAviation%20giant%20Boeing%20has%20pledged%201%20million%20dollars%20for%20the%20event.%20Google%2C%20Meta%20and%20Microsoft%20have%20said%20they%20have%20made%20similar%20donations.%20The%20list%20also%20includes%20Chevron%2C%20Amazon%20and%20Uber.%20Also%20on%20the%20list%20are%20Apple%20CEO%20Tim%20Cook%20and%20his%20OpenAI%20counterpart%20Sam%20Altman%2C%20who%20have%20pledged%20donations%20of%201%20million%20dollars%20each.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20scale%20of%20donation%20this%20time%20is%20best%20understood%20when%20in%20contrast%20to%20the%202021%20inauguration%20of%20outgoing%20President%20Joe%20Biden%2C%20which%20raised%20a%20much%20smaller%20kitty%20--%20about%2062%20million%20dollars.%20In%202017%2C%20when%20Trump%20took%20oath%20as%20President%20for%20his%20first%20term%2C%20he%20had%20raised%20a%20record%20107%20million%20dollars%2C%20which%20is%20set%20to%20be%20broken%20this%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EVIP%20Passes%20Run%20Out%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20report%20in%20The%20New%20York%20Times%2C%20several%20key%20donors%20have%20been%20told%20they%20won't%20get%20VIP%20tickets%20because%20there%20is%20no%20space.%20The%20personalised%20donation%20link%20that%20fund-raisers%20had%20circulated%20to%20their%20networks%20of%20major%20contributors%20no%20longer%20worked%20on%20Tuesday%20an