6quot%3BWe%20did%20get%20some%20payouts.%20We%20want%20to%20ask%20the%20government%2C%20it%20got%20tax.%20So%20why%20is%20it%20not%20helping%20us%20now%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20what%20made%20him%20trust%20the%20scheme%2C%20an%20investor%20said%20the%20brochure%20had%20the%20company's%20GST%20and%20CIN%20numbers.%20%26quot%3BI%20thought%20it%20is%20so%20systematic%2C%20so%20the%20government%20must%20be%20aware%20of%20this.%20I%20request%20the%20government%2C%20we%20don't%20want%20interest%2C%20but%20give%20us%20our%20money%20back.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECompany%20Claims%20Coup%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20Torres'%20official%20YouTube%20account%20uploaded%20a%20video%2C%20claiming%20that%20its%20CEO%20led%20a%20coup%20and%20facilitated%20robbery%20at%20the%20company's%20showrooms.%20%26quot%3BUnder%20the%20leadership%20of%20two%20Torres%20employees%2C%20CEO%20Tausif%20Reyaz%20and%20Chief%20Analyst%20Abhishek%20Gupta%2C%20a%20coup%20was%20organised%20in%20the%20team%20tonight%20and%20Torres%20stores%20were%20robbed%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20voiceover%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20video%20shows%20people%20vandalising%20stores%20and%20robbing%20money.%20The%20voiceover%20described%20these%20people%20as%20%26quot%3Baccomplices%26quot%3B%20of%20Reyaz%20and%20Gupta.%20%26quot%3BEarlier%2C%20we%20learnt%20that%20they%20organised%20a%20fraudulent%20scheme%20and%20systematically%20appropriated%20the%20company's%20money%20for%20many%20months...%20Realising%20that%20punishment%20was%20inevitable%20for%20them%2C%20they%20decided%20to%20involve%20other%20employees%20in%20their%20crime%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736661000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fj7v7u5i8_ukraine-torres-scam-mumbai-_625x300_12_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftorres-scam-torres-ponzi-scheme-in-mumbais-torres-jewellery-scam-investigators-une