me%20experience.%20But%20for%20me%2C%20waking%20up%20on%20a%20frigid%20March%20morning%20in%201998%2C%20I%20was%20ready%20to%20go.%20It%20was%20our%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fno-screen-time-road-trips-rule-kids-audiobooks-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Efirst%20family%20road%20trip%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20and%20we%20were%20headed%20down%20to%20my%20grandparents'%20Condo%20in%20Marco%20Island%2C%20Florida.%20And%2C%20in%20what%20was%20probably%20a%20bid%20to%20keep%20me%20quiet%2C%20my%20parents%20had%20bought%20me%20a%20brand%20new%20Gameboy%20with%20Pok%C3%A9mon%20%E2%80%94%20I%20was%20raring%20to%20go.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20didn't%20know%20it%20yet%2C%20but%20this%20was%20the%20first%20step%20in%20what%20would%20become%20one%20of%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffamily-travel-tips-for-road-trips-international-vacations-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Emost%20significant%20annual%20events%20of%20my%20entire%20life%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2271d2519d-7d80-456d-97b1-917697c9a79a%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20would%20drive%20from%20Canada%20to%20Florida%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEach%20year%2C%20March%20Break%20became%20defined%20by%20heading%20from%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-things-to-do-canada-photos-2017-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eour%20home%20in%20Ottawa%2C%20Canada%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20down%20to%20%26quot%3BThe%20Condo%26quot%3B%20(it%20achieved%20proper%20noun%20status%20in%20my%20family%20long%20ago)%20%E2%80%94%20the%20year-round%20balmy%20Florida%20weather%20a%20welcome%20and%20almost%20magical%20contrast%20to%20the%20iced-over%20roads%20and%20gray%20skies%20of%20Ottawa%20in%20March.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20grandparents%20bought%20the%20condo%20after%20they%20retired%20in%20the%20early%2090s%2C%20and%20my%20childhood%20winters%20became%20punctuated%20by%20two%20weeks%20of%20glorious%20heat%20each%20year.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOur%20first%20day%20often%20ended%20in%20Roanoke%2C%20Virginia%2C%20an%20infamous%20place%20in%20our%20family%20lore.%20This%20was%20mostly%20because%20we%20were%20all%20motion%20sick%20from%20our%20first%20day%20spent%20in%20a%20car%2C%20inevitably%20throwing%20up%20on%20our%20only%20night%20in%20town.%20Day%20two%20usually%20ended%20in%20Orlando%20or%20Tampa%20Bay%2C%20staying%20over%20so%20we%20kids%20could%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnyc-to-disney-world-and-back-in-24-hours-costs-photos-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eexhaust%20ourselves%20at%20Disney%20World%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20Universal%20Studios%2C%20or%2C%20eventually%2C%20the%20Kennedy%20Space%20Center.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOver%20the%20years%2C%20the%20story%20remained%20the%20same%2C%20even%20if%20the%20details%20changed%3A%20early%20start%2C%20sick%20in%20Virginia%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-game-boy-games-2019-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehours%20lost%20on%20a%20Gameboy%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20and%20spending%20a%20couple%20of%20days%20at%20theme%20parks%20before%20heading%20to%20the%20Condo.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22026becab-0ef1-4904-af25-a5c5cba6091d%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20felt%20like%20the%20place%20just%20belonged%20to%20us%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20me%2C%20Marco%20Island%20was%20a%20place%20that%20felt%20as%20personal%20as%20someone%20else's%20secret%20family%20recipe.%20It%20was%20a%20place%20only%20for%20us%3A%20nobody%20outside%20our%20family%20had%20ever%20even%20heard%20of%20it.%20A%20small%20retirement%20community%20on%20the%20shores%20of%20the%20Gulf%20of%20Mexico%2C%20today%20there%20are%20still%20fewer%20than%2020%2C000%20residents.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20years%20since%20our%20first%20trip%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-us-beach-towns-2017-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EMarco%20Island%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20has%20been%20at%20the%20center%20of%20dozens%20of%20core%20memories%3A%20few%20were%20more%20iconic%20than%20splashing%20around%20in%20the%20pool%20as%20thickly-accented%20Bostonian%20snowbirds%20scowled%20their%20way%20through%20calisthenics%20sessions%20at%20us.%20Inevitably%2C%20we%20were%20the%20only%20kids%20in%20the%20complex%20aside%20from%20a%20couple%20of%20others%20who%20were%20visiting%20their%20grandparents%20too%20%E2%80%94%20we'd%20quickly%20make%20and%20forget%20our%20new%20friends%20each%20year%2C%20united%20in%20our%20days'%20long-shared%20experience%20of%20being%20under%20five%20feet%20tall.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECountless%20embarrassing%20photos%20have%20been%20taken%20(and%20hopefully%20lost)%2C%20including%20my%20spot-on%20imitation%20of%20a%20pelican%20loitering%20around%20our%20favorite%20restaurant%2C%20the%20aptly-named%20Pelican%20Bend.%20The%20first%20time%20I%20was%20ever%20allowed%20to%20stay%20up%20until%20midnight%20was%20at%20the%20Condo%20on%20Y2K%2C%20watching%20the%20Nickelodeon%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3Ecoverage%20of%20the%20big%20event.%20Teaching%20my%20younger%20sister%20how%20to%20play%20mini-golf%2C%20taking%20my%20first%20flight%20without%20my%20parents%20when%20I%20visited%20in%20my%2020s.%20I%20even%20introduced%20my%20future%20wife%20on%20a%20video%20call%20to%20my%20grandparents%20while%20I%20was%20staying%20over%20at%20the%20condo%20(%26quot%3BShe's%20a%2010!%26quot%3B%20my%20grandmother%20exclaimed).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f127a6b1-6af7-4933-a488-d062367da819%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20wa