nipur%2C%20often%20referred%20to%20as%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F359452%2Fflower-gardening-business-portulaca-farming-by-kerala-alappuzha-engineer-making-lakhs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20%E2%80%9Cland%20of%20flowers%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20is%20known%20for%20its%20lush%2C%20organic%20produce%20and%20its%20people%E2%80%99s%20love%20for%20nature.%20Chokhone%20Krichena%2C%20the%2032-year-old%20founder%20of%20Dianthe%20Pvt.%20Ltd.%2C%20is%20leveraging%20these%20sentiments%20to%20help%20floriculture%20farmers%20by%20bridging%20the%20gap%20between%20rural%20growers%20and%20urban%20consumers.%20By%20helping%20backend%20farmers%20get%20market%20access%2C%20she%20is%20giving%20them%20a%20means%20to%20safely%20grow%20their%20flowers%20and%20sell%20them%20at%20a%20fair%20price%2C%20driving%20the%20local%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%222400846096%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20a%20hobby%20to%20a%20business%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChokhone%E2%80%99s%20journey%20into%20floriculture%20was%20not%20a%20sudden%20one%2C%20but%20rather%20a%20story%20of%20rediscovery.%20Growing%20up%20in%20a%20farming%20family%2C%20she%20was%20always%20surrounded%20by%20agriculture%2C%20even%20though%20her%20family%E2%80%99s%20land%20was%20not%20suitable%20for%20large-scale%20commercial%20farming.%20The%20hilly%20terrain%20of%20Mao%20makes%20it%20difficult%20for%20farmers%20to%20grow%20cash%20crops.%20Instead%2C%20most%20people%20cultivate%20fruits%20and%20vegetables%20using%20traditional%2C%20sometimes%20primitive%20methods.%20Despite%20this%2C%20there%20was%20always%20an%20air%20of%20possibility%20in%20the%20village%20%E2%80%94%20and%20for%20Chokhon