0ever%20eager%20to%20expand%20and%20provide%20more%20opportunities.%20Her%20son%2C%20Shangreiphao%2C%20shares%20his%20mother%E2%80%99s%20pride%20and%20determination.%20The%20lessons%20he%20has%20gleaned%20from%20Yangmila%20%E2%80%94%20of%20perseverance%2C%20tenacity%2C%20and%20consistency%20%E2%80%94%20are%20treasures%20he%20holds%20dear.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FShirin-Products-3-1735194438.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Shangreiphao%20says%20he%20has%20learned%20the%20true%20meaning%20of%20consistency%20and%20perseverance%20from%20his%20mother.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FShirin-Products-3-1735194438.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FShirin-Products-3-1735194438-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FShirin-Products-3-1735194438-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FShirin-Products-3-1735194438-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FShirin-Products-3-1735194438-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-392608%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EShangreiphao%20says%20he%20has%20learned%20the%20true%20meaning%20of%20consistency%20and%20perseverance%20from%20his%20mother.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20%3Cem%3Eava%20%3C%2Fem%3E(mother)%20is%20a%20very%20strong%20woman.%20Despite%20her%20age%2C%20she%20stays%20dedicated%20to%20her%20work%20and%20never%20forgets%20the%20techniques%2C%20methods%2C%20or%20the%20precise%20ratio%20of%20ingredients%20to%20use.%20From%20her%2C%20I%E2%80%99ve%20learned%20the%20true%20meaning%20of%20consistency%20and%20perseverance%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Shangreiphao%2C%20who%20pursued%20a%20master%E2%80%99s%20in%20forestry.%20%E2%80%9CAlthough%20she%E2%80%99s%20a%20dropout%20herself%2C%20she%20understands%20the%20value%20of%20education.%20It%20was%20she%20who%20insisted%20that%20I%20study%20further.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Yangmila%2C%20her%20journey%20is%20also%20about%20redefining%20societal%20norms%20and%20breaking%20the%20chains%20of%20limitations%20imposed%20by%20circumstances.%20Her%20message%20to%20women%20in%20similar%20straits%20is%20clear%3A%20%E2%80%9CDo%20not%20feel%20bogged%20down%20by%20what%20happens%20to%20you.%20Nurture%20the%20talent%20given%20to%20you%20by%20God%3B%20be%20strong%20and%20courageous%2C%20and%20good%20things%20will%20happen.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20All%20images%20courtesy%20Shangreiphao%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736307000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FShirin-Products-1-1735194242.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D392533%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22At%2021%2C%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20Yangmila%20Zimik%20overcame%20societal%20stigma%20and%20financial%20challenges%20as%20a%20single%20mother%2C%20turning%20her%20entrepreneurial%20journey%20into%20a%20thriving%20food%20brand%2C%20'Shirin%20Products'.%20From%20crafting%20candies%20and%20pickles%20using%20local%20wild%20fruits%20to%20empowering%20farmers%20and%20women%2C%20here%E2%80%99s%20how%20her%20resilience%20and%20innovation%20have%20earned%20her%20national%20recognition.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F392533%2Fsingle-mom-yangmila-zimik-manipur-food-business-wild-fruits-candies-pickles-shirin-products%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%223%20School%20Friends%20Turned%20Entrepreneurs%20Are%20Helping%20Rajasthan%E2%80%99s%20Farmers%20Earn%20Profits%20With%20%E2%80%98Foreka%E2%80%99%20Oils%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ELow%20wages%20and%20the%20relentless%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F363341%2Fdelhi-police-constable-amit-lathia-teaches-underprivileged-low-income-children-for-competitive-exam-helps-get-govt-job%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecycle%20of%20poverty%3C%2Fa%3E%20force%20many%20farmers%20in%20Rajasthan%20to%20leave%20their%20families%20and%20seek%20better%20opportunities%20elsewhere.%20Their%20children%2C%20innocent%20victims%20of%20circumstance%2C%20are%20often%20forced%20to%20discontinue%20their%20education.%20Three%20young%20entrepreneurs%2C%20Satyam%20Bhandari%2C%20Rohit%20Negi%2C%20and%20Mohit%20Rana%2C%20were%20determined%20to%20change%20this%2C%20and%20through%20grit%20and%20hard%20work%2C%20they%20founded%20Foreka%2C%20a%20company%20that%20aimed%20to%20empower%20these%20farmers%20and%20uplift%20their%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20watched%20my%20mother%20struggle%20to%20become%20financially%20empowered%20so%20she%20could%20give%20me%20a%20better%20life%2C%20and%20that%20inspired%20me%20deeply.%20As%20I%20connected%20with%20farmers%20and%20tribals%2C%20I%20was%20reminded%20of%20her%20struggles.%20I%20knew%20I%20had%20to%20do%20something%20for%20them%2C%20to%20ensure%20they%20too%20could%20have%20equal%20opportunities%2C%E2%80%9D%20Satyam%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20and%20raised%20in%20Agastyamuni%2C%20a%20peaceful%20town%20cradled%20in%20the%20foothills%20of%20the%20Himalayas%2C%20Satyam%2C%20who%20lost%20his%20father%20six%20days%20before%20he%20was%20born%2C%20had%20seen%20his%20mother%20work%20tirelessly%20to%20manage%20the%20household%20and%20raise%20him%20on%20her%20own.%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20thankful%20to%20her%20for%20ensuring%20I%20attended%20a%20good%20school%20and%20for%20gi