%2FIMG_0520-1734611729.jpg%20600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG_0520-1734611729-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG_0520-1734611729-500x333.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG_0520-1734611729-150x100.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-391008%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22400%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20SIP%20Memorial%20Trust%20provides%20a%20comfortable%20home%20for%20children%20who%20have%20tested%20positive%20for%20HIV.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20comfortable%20at%20SIP%20home%20as%20I%20used%20to%20get%20healthy%20and%20delicious%20meals%20every%20day.%20I%20also%20had%20my%20friends%2C%20with%20whom%20time%20would%20fly%20away%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Naga%2C%20sharing%20the%20joy%20of%20growing%20in%20the%20safe%20space%20created%20by%20Noori.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20proud%20to%20say%20that%20I%20am%20the%20first%20transgender%20to%20own%20a%20passport%20and%20a%20ration%20card%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Noori%2C%20who%20currently%20holds%2022%20leadership%20positions%20for%20multiple%20organisations%20and%20welfare%20boards.%20She%20has%20been%20the%20Coordinator%20of%20the%20South%20Asia%20TIDES%20Foundation%20(2005%20to%202008)%2C%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Transgender%20Welfare%20Board%20(2008)%2C%20and%20Vice%20President%20of%20India%20People%20Alliance%20Combating%20HIV%2FAIDS%20(IPACHA)%2C%202009.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20society%20is%20more%20inclusive%20and%20aware%20of%20the%20difficulties%20faced%20by%20transgenders%20and%20people%20who%20are%20affected%20by%20HIV.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20medical%20advancements%20help%20in%20taking%20care%20of%20the%20physical%20aspects%2C%20and%20a%20comparatively%20understanding%20society%20makes%20the%20battles%20a%20little%20easy%